name: markdown-documentation-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for organizing and writing Markdown documentation for AI in the project
globs: "*.md"

- Use Markdown files exclusively for AI documentation, not for end-users
- Optimize structure for AI information processing
- Describe functionality and structure, not actual code
- Use English for technical component names
- Ensure clear hierarchical structure with headings
- Write concisely to optimize token usage while maintaining completeness 